LARSH 1
w 256
h 192
fps 12
bg 0x1a1a2e
loop

obj 0 rect 20 80 60 40 0xe94560
obj 1 circle 200 96 25 0x0f3460
obj 2 text 80 4 "Hello LardOS" 0xeaeaea
obj 3 lmd 8 24 240 160 0xeaeaea "# LMD Demo
- **bold** text
- `code` style
- List items"

key 0 0 x 20
key 60 0 x 180
key 120 0 x 20
key 0 1 x 200
key 60 1 x 56
key 120 1 x 200
